{"tid":1768378,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"叱咤樂壇流行榜頒獎典禮取消","createTime":"2019-12-04T04:27:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T05:28:42.000Z","uid":241764,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e03e0fefd3563c1c6208d4f223f24f57308b0ab8","tid":1768378,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T04:27:28.000Z","msg":"商業電台一直堅定不移支持本地樂壇，並以獎項嘉許努力不懈的音樂人，感謝樂迷一直支持每年一月一日的叱咤樂壇流行榜頒獎典禮。<br />\n<br />\n多個月來，我們努力研究不同方案，希望能確保2020年1月1日頒獎禮當日所有參與者場外場內之安全，抱歉至今仍未找到最妥善的方法，故只好無奈取消原定於灣仔會展新翼舉行之頒獎典禮，並改以其他形式頒發全數共43個叱咤獎項。<br />\n<br />\n「樂迷投票」部分已經開始，並將會繼續進行，我最喜愛的男、女歌手和組合獎項會如常於網上投票；我最喜愛的歌曲獎項最後階段之現場投票部分，則改在12月23日至27日於網上進行，以貫徹「專業推介，樂迷投票」的叱咤精神。<br />\n<br />\n本年叱咤的主題為「學樂樂學」，我們將繼續努力學習。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/8792258557/posts/10157302580493558\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F8792258557%2Fposts%2F10157302580493558&d=sHvBfS5bCv0nfD6zjI7mDbO6ciNacqKxYXGqE8pVUEM%3D&h=1432207c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/8792258557/posts/10157302580493558</a>"},{"pid":"2ea468fa017ecb7e29b6f71152c816bd2ccf3240","tid":1768378,"uid":202122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T04:27:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82cd29824daffba60366f65d061897dc98a1a883","tid":1768378,"uid":153679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T04:28:03.000Z","msg":"噢。"},{"pid":"4423ab2475be8e791bd3492890b725bf946de889","tid":1768378,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T04:28:43.000Z","msg":"港共比壓力？"},{"pid":"a0aa7955d595322b744f73d7438c9d67b85efa58","tid":1768378,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0